{"tid":1409566,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［國際文宣］social media campaign 有無得諗？","createTime":"2019-08-04T22:35:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T03:30:07.000Z","uid":269054,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9cb0e176b5896a0b389bc1546c24bee8a04d2595","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:35:05.000Z","msg":"諗緊有咩方法可以俾多d外國人 知道同支持香港，<br />\n諗起類似 Ice bucket challenge, 或者 #metoo movement 咁叫人自已影張相再share 既玩法<br />\n<br />\n希望大家集思廣益，搞好個內容之後試吓一齊係 ig/ fb 推<br />\n<br />\n我先試吓拋個idea 出嚟<br />\n<br />\n#StandWithHK campaign<br />\n目標：<br />\n1. 利用社交媒體傳播引起外國人士關注香港情況<br />\n2. 鼓勵每個人參與創作，分享，感染其他人<br />\n3. 鼓勵更多行動，例如英國美國人參與聯署，要求其議會代表通過有關改善香港民主的法案等。"},{"pid":"c89d68fad24cd7f323eababe1e5c52e3e522c5fa","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:38:46.000Z","msg":"玩法：<br />\n1. 嘗試扮作一個香港示威者，影一張相/video。<br />\n2. 連同本message 放係自己ig/Facebook/ Twitter. <br />\n3. tag 5個人，請求佢一齊參與。<br />\n4. 參加聯署，幫助香港人尋求國際協助。<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n如何扮一個香港示威者創作指引：<br />\n<br />\n1. 制作一張標語，寫你想講既野同埋有#StandWithHK hashtag <br />\n2. 開摭 - 代表香港人自雨傘運動開始對 #真普選 的訴求<br />\n3. 摭面 - 香港的示威者大多隱藏身份，因為害怕&lsquo;白色恐怖&rsquo;，政治檢控，甚至10年的監禁。<br />\n4. 戴防具 - 香港人及記者都要面對警察濫用武力及黑社會襲擊，需要帶安全帽，眼罩，口罩等日常用具保護自己。<br />\n5. 發揮創意 - 香港人靈活變通，無論面對任何打壓都會一一化解，直至落實真雙普選。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n英國公民請參與聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petition.standwithhk.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetition.standwithhk.org%2F&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoWCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=82fe7aed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petition.standwithhk.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國公民聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Factionnetwork.org%2Fletters%2Fco-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoWCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=86b13e83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://actionnetwork.org/letters/co-sponsor-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-of-2019</a><br />\n<br />\n國際人士可聯署美國白宮聯署<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act&d=nzz81mtU0v8QN53TvL9QoWCkd6W2E%2BSZ990UparCCSw%3D&h=70e8e2cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act</a><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-"},{"pid":"de97f49b82df3ca2adef4164a35a0f052ca481d6","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:03.000Z","msg":"自推十下"},{"pid":"fdb43dd866197589847279f9e16b866db62e4efc","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5ed1205ef3e3418846096adc9827a7ccc26aa024","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:23.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09e96fdffe92d8c04985e2b4f9512505d729dc06","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb114bf88786bbc31428a43930ebcd7efc4eb87a","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:47:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"87ac7a78a0949fb4177442c1b1a2007a013dc901","tid":1409566,"uid":269054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T22:48:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fb7baabc3701e58aad9eea04f42ef6e40c092db1","tid":1409566,"uid